          CALL            FOR                        PARTICIPATION


                          LPAR 2003

          September 22-26th, 2003, Almaty, Kazakhstan

                   http://www.lpar.net/2003/



International Conference on
  Logic for
  Programming
  Artificial Intelligence and
  Reasoning


PROGRAM CHAIRS

